variable.name: PLATE_ID
variable.comment: Character field Blank = Field not filled in. Non-blank = Field filled in.

variable.name: BCHE_I
variable.value: Set to missing because CV was above allowable limit

variable.name: MCAM_I
variable.description: Indicator variable for melanoma cell adhesion molecule (MCAM)
variable.value: Set to missing because CV was above allowable limit

variable.name: BCHE
variable.comment: The lower detectable limit for BCHE is 1.07E+05 pg/mL and the upper detectable limit is 4.66E+08 pg/mL. BCHE values below or above these limits were set to the lower or upper detectable limit respectively. Use BCHE_I to see what records are below and above these limits. BCHE values were set to unknown if BCHE_CV was greater than or equal to 42.5 for Offspring (IDTYPE = 1) or 37.2 for Gen 3 (IDTYPE = 3).

variable.name: BCHE_CV
variable.comment: BCHE_CV values were set to unknown if BCHE_CV was greater than or equal to 42.5 for Offspring (IDTYPE = 1) or 37.2 for Gen 3 (IDTYPE = 3).

variable.name: MCAM
variable.description: Melanoma cell adhesion molecule (MCAM) (sample type: plasma)
variable.comment: The lower detectable limit for MCAM is 3.36E+03 pg/mL and the upper detectable limit is 1.39E+07 pg/mL. MCAM values below or above these limits were set to the lower or upper detectable limit respectively. Use MCAM_I to see what records are below and above these limits. MCAM values were set to unknown if MCAM_CV was greater than or equal to 35.0 for Offspring (IDTYPE = 1) or 30.2 for Gen 3 (IDTYPE = 3).

variable.name: MCAM_CV
variable.description: CV for melanoma cell adhesion molecule (MCAM)
variable.comment: MCAM_CV values were set to unknown if MCAM_CV was greater than or equal to 35.0 for Offspring (IDTYPE = 1) or 30.2 for Gen 3 (IDTYPE = 3).

variable.name: RUN_DATE
variable.comment: Date includes month, day and year, however, coding manual displays only month and year to preserve confidentiality.
